[2.009, "o", "Deployment successful! The script:\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  1. Generated Counter with a typed constructor arg (initial=123)\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  2. Started a local Anvil chain\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  3. Sent initcode via cast send --create\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  4. Verified deployed runtime code matches Counter.bin\r\n  5. Ran the Counter lifecycle through JSON-RPC\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  6. Wrote a deploy-run artifact for validation\r\n"]
